edu.stanford.cs.pptx

Class PPShow

  • Object
    • edu.stanford.cs.pptx.PPShow

  • public class PPShow
extends Object
    This class represents a complete PowerPoint slide show, which consists of a sequence of slides. To ensure that the numbering of slides in the data structure matches the conventional numbering scheme of a PowerPoint presentation, the numbering begins at 1.
